Subject: [PATCH 641/691] ENGR00234353-2: mx6q_sabreauto_weimnor fix redundant
 env offset

* Fix redundant enviroment offset
* Disable I2C support as they share pads
* Enable flash empty information
* weim-nor partition layout
  +-----------------+ 0x08000000
  +      u-boot     +
  +-----------------+ 0x08040000 (256k)
  +    u-boot env   +
  +-----------------+ 0x08060000 (128k)
  + u-boot redundat +
  +-----------------+ 0x08080000 (128k)
  +     Kernel      +
  +-----------------+ 0x08480000 (4M)
  +     Rootfs      +
  +-----------------+ (~27M)

Signed-off-by: Adrian Alonso <aalonso@freescale.com>
